[[!meta title="""Smuxi 1.0 "Finally" Release"""]]

Smuxi 1.0 with persistent chat history, persistent message markers/counters,
single application instance support and NickServ support. Packages are available
for Windows, Mac OS X and Debian (Sid).  Here you can read the
[full release announcement][1]. For users running a development build of Smuxi
it is recommended to simply upgrade to the newest [development build][2].

  [1]: https://smuxi.im/news/smuxi_1.0_release/
  [2]: https://smuxi.im/documentation/running-from-git/
